# Unicode.GeneralCategory.otherNumber

**Case**

A numeric character of another type.

## Declaration

```swift
case otherNumber
```

## Discussion

This value corresponds to the category `Other_Number` (abbreviated `No`) in the [https://unicode.org/reports/tr44/#General_Category_Values].
